lead_paragraph: Justine Henin dispatched Andreja Klepac, 6-3, 6-1, but Ana Ivanovic’s title defense ended yesterday when she lost to Zi Yan, the 169th-ranked player in the world, in the second round of the Rogers Cup in Toronto. No. 5 Anna Chakvetadze and No. 8 Elena Dementieva were eliminated.
